<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Isaac Lindell</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Spectral:ital,wght@0,200;0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;1,200;1,300;1,400;1,500;1,600&family=Cinzel:wght@400;500;600&family=EB+Garamond:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;1,400;1,500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

/* ─── TOKENS ─── */
:root {
  --green:       #1B3D2A;
  --green-deep:  #142D1F;
  --green-mid:   #2A5040;
  --gold:        #C8B87A;
  --gold-dim:    rgba(200,184,122,0.45);
  --gold-faint:  rgba(200,184,122,0.15);
  --ivory:       #FAFAF7;
  --ivory-mid:   #F2F0EC;
  --ivory-dark:  #E8E4DC;
  --ink:         #1A1810;
  --ink-mid:     #2E2A22;
  --ink-light:   #6B6355;
  --ink-faint:   #A09888;
  --white:       #FDFCF9;
  --rule:        rgba(26,24,16,0.1);
}

html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

body {
  background: #FAFAF7;
  color: var(--ink);
  font-family: 'Spectral', Georgia, serif;
  font-weight: 300;
  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
}

/* ══════════════════════════════════════
   NAV — The Oxford Statement
══════════════════════════════════════ */
.site-nav {
  background: var(--green);
  position: sticky;
  top: 0;
  z-index: 100;
  box-shadow: 0 2px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.18);
}

.nav-inner {
  max-width: 1200px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 0 2.5rem;
  display: flex;
  align-items: stretch;
  justify-content: space-between;
  min-height: 58px;
}

.nav-left {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: center;
  padding: 0.8rem 0;
  gap: 0.2rem;
}

.nav-logo {
  font-family: 'Spectral', serif;
  font-size: 1.15rem;
  font-weight: 300;
  color: var(--ivory);
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  line-height: 1;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: color 0.2s;
}
.nav-logo:hover { color: var(--gold); }
.nav-logo em {
  font-style: italic;
  font-weight: 200;
  color: rgba(245,240,232,0.7);
}

.nav-gold-rule {
  width: 100%;
  height: 1px;
  background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--gold), transparent);
  opacity: 0.6;
}

.nav-tabs {
  display: flex;
  align-items: stretch;
}

.nav-tab {
  font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
  font-size: 0.57rem;
  font-weight: 400;
  letter-spacing: 0.22em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: rgba(245,240,232,0.45);
  padding: 0 1.2rem;
  border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all 0.2s;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  border-top: 2px solid transparent;
}
.nav-tab:hover { color: rgba(245,240,232,0.8); }
.nav-tab.active {
  color: var(--ivory);
  border-bottom-color: var(--gold);
}

/* ══════════════════════════════════════
   HOMEPAGE — LIST VIEW
══════════════════════════════════════ */
#view-home {
  display: block;
}
#view-article {
  display: none;
}

.home-wrap {
  max-width: 1200px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 0 2.5rem;
}

/* Section heading */
.section-head {
  padding: 3rem 0 2rem;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
  display: flex;
  align-items: baseline;
  justify-content: space-between;
}
.section-title {
  font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
  font-size: 0.6rem;
  font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: 0.35em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--ink-faint);
}
.section-count {
  font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
  font-size: 0.52rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.2em;
  color: var(--gold);
}

/* Featured — first article large */
.featured-post {
  padding: 3rem 0 2.5rem;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: background 0.2s;
}
.featured-post:hover .post-title { color: var(--green); }

.featured-inner {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 340px;
  gap: 4rem;
  align-items: start;
}

.post-kicker {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.7rem;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}
.post-kicker-line {
  width: 20px;
  height: 1px;
  background: var(--gold);
}
.post-kicker-text {
  font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
  font-size: 0.52rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.28em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--gold);
}

.post-title {
  font-family: 'Spectral', serif;
  font-size: 2.8rem;
  font-weight: 200;
  line-height: 1.05;
  color: var(--ink);
  letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  transition: color 0.2s;
}
.post-title em {
  font-style: italic;
  font-weight: 300;
}

.post-dateline {
  font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
  font-size: 0.52rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.2em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--ink-faint);
  margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
}

.post-excerpt {
  font-size: 1rem;
  line-height: 1.82;
  color: var(--ink-mid);
  font-weight: 300;
  max-width: 560px;
}

.post-read-more {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.6rem;
  margin-top: 1.5rem;
  font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
  font-size: 0.52rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.25em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--green);
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: gap 0.2s;
}
.post-read-more:hover { gap: 0.9rem; }
.post-read-more-arrow {
  width: 20px;
  height: 1px;
  background: var(--green);
  position: relative;
}
.post-read-more-arrow::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  right: 0;
  top: -3px;
  width: 6px;
  height: 6px;
  border-right: 1px solid var(--green);
  border-top: 1px solid var(--green);
  transform: rotate(45deg);
}

/* Featured right — pull quote / meta */
.featured-aside {
  padding-top: 0.5rem;
}
.aside-rule {
  width: 1px;
  height: 100%;
  background: var(--rule);
  display: none;
}
.aside-label {
  font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
  font-size: 0.5rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.3em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--ink-faint);
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}
.aside-pullquote {
  font-family: 'Spectral', serif;
  font-size: 1.2rem;
  font-weight: 200;
  font-style: italic;
  color: var(--ink-mid);
  line-height: 1.65;
  border-left: 2px solid var(--gold);
  padding-left: 1.2rem;
}
.aside-meta {
  margin-top: 1.5rem;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 0.6rem;
}
.aside-meta-item {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: baseline;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
  padding-bottom: 0.6rem;
}
.aside-meta-key {
  font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
  font-size: 0.48rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.2em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--ink-faint);
}
.aside-meta-val {
  font-size: 0.8rem;
  color: var(--ink-light);
  font-style: italic;
}

/* Post list — subsequent articles */
.post-list {
  padding: 0.5rem 0 3rem;
}

.post-item {
  padding: 2rem 0;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
  cursor: pointer;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
  gap: 2rem;
  align-items: start;
  transition: all 0.15s;
}
.post-item:hover .post-item-title { color: var(--green); }
.post-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

.post-item-kicker {
  font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
  font-size: 0.5rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.25em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--gold);
  margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
}
.post-item-title {
  font-family: 'Spectral', serif;
  font-size: 1.45rem;
  font-weight: 200;
  color: var(--ink);
  line-height: 1.2;
  margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
  transition: color 0.2s;
}
.post-item-title em { font-style: italic; }
.post-item-excerpt {
  font-size: 0.88rem;
  color: var(--ink-light);
  line-height: 1.7;
  font-weight: 300;
  max-width: 600px;
}
.post-item-date {
  font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
  font-size: 0.48rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.18em;
  color: var(--ink-faint);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  white-space: nowrap;
  padding-top: 0.3rem;
}

/* ══════════════════════════════════════
   ARTICLE VIEW — The White Sail body
══════════════════════════════════════ */
.article-wrap {
  max-width: 1200px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 0 2.5rem;
}

/* Back nav */
.article-back {
  padding: 2rem 0 0;
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.6rem;
  font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
  font-size: 0.52rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.22em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--ink-faint);
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: color 0.2s, gap 0.2s;
}
.article-back:hover { color: var(--green); gap: 0.35rem; }
.back-arrow {
  width: 18px;
  height: 1px;
  background: currentColor;
  position: relative;
}
.back-arrow::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  left: 0;
  top: -3px;
  width: 6px;
  height: 6px;
  border-left: 1px solid currentColor;
  border-bottom: 1px solid currentColor;
  transform: rotate(45deg);
}

/* Article header */
.article-header {
  padding: 2.5rem 0 2rem;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
  max-width: 820px;
}

.article-kicker {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.7rem;
  margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
}
.article-kicker-line {
  width: 20px;
  height: 1px;
  background: var(--gold);
}
.article-kicker-text {
  font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
  font-size: 0.52rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.28em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--gold);
}

.article-title {
  font-family: 'Spectral', serif;
  font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 5vw, 3.8rem);
  font-weight: 200;
  line-height: 1.0;
  color: var(--ink);
  letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
}
.article-title em { font-style: italic; font-weight: 300; }

.article-dateline {
  font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
  font-size: 0.52rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.22em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--ink-faint);
  margin-top: 0.8rem;
}

/* Article body layout */
.article-body-wrap {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 240px;
  gap: 5rem;
  padding: 3rem 0 5rem;
  align-items: start;
}

/* The White Sail body text */
.article-body {
  font-family: 'Spectral', serif;
  font-size: 1.05rem;
  line-height: 1.9;
  color: var(--ink-mid);
  font-weight: 300;
}

.article-body p {
  margin-bottom: 1.6em;
}

.article-body p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

/* Section break */
.article-break {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.75rem;
  margin: 2.5rem 0;
}
.article-break-line {
  flex: 1;
  height: 1px;
  background: var(--rule);
}
.article-break-diamond {
  width: 5px;
  height: 5px;
  background: var(--gold);
  transform: rotate(45deg);
  opacity: 0.6;
}

/* Article sidebar */
.article-sidebar {
  position: sticky;
  top: 80px;
}

.sidebar-about {
  padding: 1.5rem 0;
  border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
}
.sidebar-label {
  font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
  font-size: 0.5rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.28em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--ink-faint);
  margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
}
.sidebar-author {
  font-family: 'Spectral', serif;
  font-size: 0.88rem;
  font-weight: 300;
  color: var(--ink-light);
  line-height: 1.65;
  font-style: italic;
}

.sidebar-more {
  border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
  padding-top: 1.5rem;
}
.sidebar-more-item {
  padding: 0.9rem 0;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
  cursor: pointer;
}
.sidebar-more-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
.sidebar-more-item:hover .sidebar-more-title { color: var(--green); }
.sidebar-more-kicker {
  font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
  font-size: 0.46rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.22em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--gold);
  margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
}
.sidebar-more-title {
  font-family: 'Spectral', serif;
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  font-weight: 300;
  font-style: italic;
  color: var(--ink-mid);
  line-height: 1.3;
  transition: color 0.2s;
}

/* ── FOOTER ── */
.site-footer {
  background: var(--green-deep);
  padding: 2.5rem;
}
.footer-inner {
  max-width: 1200px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 1rem;
}
.footer-logo {
  font-family: 'Spectral', serif;
  font-size: 1rem;
  font-weight: 200;
  color: rgba(245,240,232,0.6);
  font-style: italic;
  letter-spacing: 0.04em;
}
.footer-rule {
  flex: 1;
  height: 1px;
  background: rgba(200,184,122,0.15);
  margin: 0 2rem;
  min-width: 40px;
}
.footer-copy {
  font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
  font-size: 0.48rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.22em;
  color: rgba(200,184,122,0.35);
  text-transform: uppercase;
}

/* ── TRANSITIONS ── */
#view-home, #view-article {
  animation: fadeUp 0.35s ease both;
}
@keyframes fadeUp {
  from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); }
  to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}

/* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
@media (max-width: 860px) {
  .featured-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .featured-aside { display: none; }
  .article-body-wrap { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .article-sidebar { display: none; }
  .post-title { font-size: 2rem; }
  .nav-inner { padding: 0 1.5rem; }
  .home-wrap, .article-wrap { padding: 0 1.5rem; }
  .site-footer { padding: 2rem 1.5rem; }
}

/* ── LABEL BAR (for the mockup context) ── */
.mockup-label {
  background: #EEEBE4;
  padding: 0.65rem 2.5rem;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ivory-mid);
}
.ml-name {
  font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
  font-size: 0.55rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.25em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: #888;
}
.ml-switch {
  display: flex;
  gap: 0.5rem;
}
.ml-btn {
  font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
  font-size: 0.5rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.18em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem;
  border: 1px solid var(--ivory-dark);
  background: transparent;
  color: #888;
  cursor: pointer;
  border-radius: 2px;
  transition: all 0.2s;
}
.ml-btn.active, .ml-btn:hover {
  background: var(--green);
  color: var(--ivory);
  border-color: var(--green);
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- mockup context label -->
<div class="mockup-label">
  <span class="ml-name">The Oxford × White Sail — Final Hybrid</span>
  <div class="ml-switch">
    <button class="ml-btn active" onclick="showView('home', this)">Homepage</button>
    <button class="ml-btn" onclick="showView('article', this)">Article View</button>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════
     NAVIGATION
══════════════════════════════════════ -->
<nav class="site-nav">
  <div class="nav-inner">
    <div class="nav-left" onclick="showView('home', null)">
      <div class="nav-logo">Isaac <em>Lindell</em></div>
      <div class="nav-gold-rule"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="nav-tabs">
      <div class="nav-tab active" onclick="switchTab(this, 'Short Stories')">Short Stories</div>
      <div class="nav-tab" onclick="switchTab(this, 'Think Pieces')">Think Pieces</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════
     HOMEPAGE VIEW
══════════════════════════════════════ -->
<div id="view-home">
  <div class="home-wrap">

    <div class="section-head">
      <span class="section-title" id="section-label">Short Stories</span>
      <span class="section-count">7 pieces</span>
    </div>

    <!-- Featured post -->
    <div class="featured-post" onclick="showView('article', null)">
      <div class="featured-inner">
        <div>
          <div class="post-kicker">
            <div class="post-kicker-line"></div>
            <span class="post-kicker-text">Featured · Fiction</span>
          </div>
          <h1 class="post-title">Dirt</h1>
          <div class="post-dateline">Wyoming Desert &nbsp;·&nbsp; August 1958 &nbsp;·&nbsp; 6 min read</div>
          <p class="post-excerpt">The best. That's what he wanted — nothing subpar, nothing lesser; only prestige, simply masterclass. It was hard to please Dr. Carvill. The butterflies in Paisley's stomach were not from nervous excitement. No, the last time she felt those was when Brady Jenkins asked her to the Junior Prom.</p>
          <div class="post-read-more">
            <span>Read</span>
            <div class="post-read-more-arrow"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="featured-aside">
          <div class="aside-label">From the piece</div>
          <div class="aside-pullquote">"Perhaps this is normal," she thought. Heading into the middle of the Wyoming desert with a guy you met last week.</div>
          <div class="aside-meta">
            <div class="aside-meta-item">
              <span class="aside-meta-key">Category</span>
              <span class="aside-meta-val">Short Fiction</span>
            </div>
            <div class="aside-meta-item">
              <span class="aside-meta-key">Published</span>
              <span class="aside-meta-val">November 2025</span>
            </div>
            <div class="aside-meta-item">
              <span class="aside-meta-key">Read time</span>
              <span class="aside-meta-val">6 minutes</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Post list -->
    <div class="post-list">

      <div class="post-item" onclick="showView('article', null)">
        <div>
          <div class="post-item-kicker">Travel · Humor</div>
          <div class="post-item-title">A Plan for the Greatest Beer Run of All Time, <em>and Why You'd Need a Passport</em></div>
          <div class="post-item-excerpt">In the olden days, explorers would seek investments from prosperous businessmen and governments to finance their grand adventures. Now consider the current day — there is nothing left to explore except in stylized, more difficult fashions.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="post-item-date">May 2025</div>
      </div>

      <div class="post-item" onclick="showView('article', null)">
        <div>
          <div class="post-item-kicker">Cultural Commentary</div>
          <div class="post-item-title">RIP Charlie Kirk</div>
          <div class="post-item-excerpt">This is an incredibly sad and frightening time for our country. A moment to sit and reflect. As small and as insignificant as my voice and this platform may be, I ask two things.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="post-item-date">September 2025</div>
      </div>

      <div class="post-item" onclick="showView('article', null)">
        <div>
          <div class="post-item-kicker">Personal Reflections</div>
          <div class="post-item-title"><em>On Reading Well in a Distracted Age</em></div>
          <div class="post-item-excerpt">There is a particular kind of silence that comes only from a good book. Not the absence of noise, but the presence of something better — a voice that asks nothing of you except attention.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="post-item-date">April 2025</div>
      </div>

      <div class="post-item" onclick="showView('article', null)">
        <div>
          <div class="post-item-kicker">Storytelling · Fiction</div>
          <div class="post-item-title">The Long Drive Home</div>
          <div class="post-item-excerpt">Some roads you drive only once. Some you drive a hundred times and never really see. This one he had driven in both ways — and today it felt like neither.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="post-item-date">March 2025</div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════
     ARTICLE VIEW
══════════════════════════════════════ -->
<div id="view-article">
  <div class="article-wrap">

    <div class="article-back" onclick="showView('home', null)">
      <div class="back-arrow"></div>
      <span>Short Stories</span>
    </div>

    <div class="article-header">
      <div class="article-kicker">
        <div class="article-kicker-line"></div>
        <span class="article-kicker-text">Short Fiction · November 2025</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="article-title">Dirt</h1>
      <div class="article-dateline">Wyoming Desert &nbsp;·&nbsp; August 9th, 1958 &nbsp;·&nbsp; 6 min read</div>
    </div>

    <div class="article-body-wrap">

      <!-- Body — The White Sail -->
      <div class="article-body">
        <p>The best. That's what he wanted. The best, nothing subpar, nothing lesser; only prestige, simply masterclass. It was hard to please Dr. Carvill.</p>

        <p>The butterflies in Paisley's stomach were not from nervous excitement. No, the last time she felt those was when Brady Jenkins asked her to the Junior Prom. These were bees, yellowjackets even, swarming rampantly. Uneasiness met with subtle, but nonetheless sharp, pangs of terror as she drove atop the dusty soil on Oil Springs Road.</p>

        <p>Despite the summer heat and dirt clinging to her sweaty skin, she felt chills, goosebumps rising on her arms and legs.</p>

        <p>Perhaps this is normal, she thought. Heading into the middle of the Wyoming desert with a guy you met last week, camping with a professor rumored to have a screw loose and a drinking problem.</p>

        <div class="article-break">
          <div class="article-break-line"></div>
          <div class="article-break-diamond"></div>
          <div class="article-break-line"></div>
        </div>

        <p>The car rattled as the pavement gave way to packed earth. She hadn't said a word to Marcus since they left Laramie, and Marcus — to his credit or discredit, she couldn't decide which — hadn't seemed to notice. He was watching the road the way men watch roads when they are thinking about something else entirely.</p>

        <p>She had taken the job because it paid well and because she had needed, desperately, to be somewhere that wasn't home. Dr. Carvill's summer research project: three weeks in the field, cataloguing geological formations. Simple enough on paper. But Dr. Carvill, she had since learned, had a talent for making simple things complicated.</p>

        <p>The camp appeared over a rise — four tents, a fire ring, a folding table with equipment she didn't recognize. Dr. Carvill was already there, standing with his back to them, looking out at something she couldn't see.</p>

        <p>He didn't turn when they pulled up. He didn't turn when they cut the engine. Only when Paisley's door squeaked open did he finally look back, and when he did, there was something in his expression she couldn't read — not quite satisfaction, not quite relief.</p>

        <p>"You're late," he said.</p>

        <p>They were, in fact, twelve minutes early.</p>
